Hey everyone,  Got some bad news. I have been suffering from issues with my heart for several years, earlier today it worsened to the extent I needed to be hospitalised. My condition had gotten significantly worse and it is hindering my work/performance, at this time I can not continue with Babymetal or any other projects. I will be having surgery soon and I need time to recuperate. I will be taking some time away( minimum one year) from music and focusing on other things. Thank you to all of the BM guys and girls, The Mashu family for taking care of me and getting me the gig, Matsumoto and Hasu for always helping out and being awesome and lastly ESP for being phenomenal. I apologise to all of the people who purchased tickets to see me, at this time I cant do anything except apologise. 
Thanks -Soroush.
